00:29:21,996 --> 00:29:25,165
My honor. My loyalty.
My respect.

255
00:29:25,299 --> 00:29:26,200
And?

256
00:29:27,501 --> 00:29:28,503
Seventy-five grand.

257
00:29:28,637 --> 00:29:30,070
There he is.
Here I am.

258
00:29:30,204 --> 00:29:32,607
