I have 75 grand?

259
00:29:32,741 --> 00:29:34,208
No.
No?

260
00:29:34,341 --> 00:29:35,442
No, you don't.

261
00:29:37,411 --> 00:29:38,946
But you do.

262
00:29:39,079 --> 00:29:41,782
